title: What to watch for from each of the 4 wrestling regions this weekend
body: Washington Township vs. Camden Catholic wrestling, March 26, 2021.The selections have been made.After marathon seeding meetings on Monday, 16 wrestlers in every weight class to take the mat in four separate regions across New Jersey as the NJSIAA/Rothman Orthopaedics wrestling tournament begins.We picked out 10 storylines in every region to focus on as the speed round of the wrestling tournament gets set to begin. Click on the links below to check them out.Note to readers: if you purchase something through one of our affiliate links we may earn a commission.
